@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>Replication Analytics</strong> is a monitoring tool for tracking replication processes in Proxmox
        VE.<br />
        It provides real-time insights into replication status, trends, and potential issues, ensuring that data synchronization across nodes remains reliable and efficient.<br />
        By analyzing historical data, it helps administrators detect anomalies and optimize replication performance.<br />
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Improved Data Resilience</strong>: Ensures that VM and CT replications function correctly, reducing the risk of data loss.<br />
        <strong>Performance Analytics</strong>: Tracks replication speed, success rates, and failure patterns to enhance efficiency.<br />
        <strong>Proactive Monitoring</strong>: Detects issues early, allowing administrators to take corrective actions before failures impact availability.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Designed for Proxmox VE with minimal setup requirements.<br />
        <strong>Historical Analysis</strong>: Provides long-term data trends to optimize replication policies.<br />
        <strong>Enhanced Troubleshooting</strong>: Helps IT teams quickly diagnose and resolve replication issues.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
